This paper deals with maintaining an approximate matching in fully dynamic graphs, which involves topics such as graph algorithms, data structures, and combinatorial optimization. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), followed by cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.NE (Networks and Economics).
